Text: "every night befor i sleep i have only one thing to start my trip (close my\
  \ eyes)\nmaybe some people will think i'm kidding or make a fun of this story ..\
  \ but i'm so series cause only when i close my eyes all my dream comes true \ni\
  \ huged the sky in my country and dance with the beards on music from the mountin\
  \ .. and playing with elephants ..\nand i travled to italy and had my favorite sbakite\
  \ meal there .. after than takes the next plane to parise to buy my perfume only\
  \ .. and back to my home \nthe true story not what we got in our life .. but it's\
  \ what we need but can't do it or get it so the best solution is dream and dream\
  \ .. one day i will take my things and travel around the world after that you will\
  \ read all my stories from my blog ."
